   By LUCIA VAN DER POST
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Making my own necklaces has not been the kind of occupational therapy that I
have ever aspired to. But Janet Coles sells beads of such beauty and
diversity that she could tempt me. Her mail order brochure is beautifully
produced - the beads presented in an ordered fashion with plenty of ideas
for creating necklaces, jewellery and bracelets, writes Lucia van der Post.
