Worcester, WR3 8QA, 0905- 755888) or from her shop, Janet Coles Bead
Emporium, 128 Notting Hill Gate, London W11. Pendants in kit form are Pounds
5, made-up about Pounds 7. Chunky necklaces cost between Pounds 9.95 and
