</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
TODAY: Meeting of foreign ministers in Geneva to decide next steps in Bosnia
peace effort.
TOMORROW: Deadline for Japan to open up public contracts in
telecommunications and medical technology purchases in order to avoid
